/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/depusdt_levusdc_p5_25_124/rounds/round_1/agent_codex_1/stdout.log:14:      "Call `approveToken(underlyingOrCToken, attacker, amount)` on the DepToken proxy.",
/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/depusdt_levusdc_p5_25_124/rounds/round_1/agent_codex_1/stdout.log:16:      "Repeat for the cUSDT balance to steal funds parked in Compound."
/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/depusdt_levusdc_p5_25_124/rounds/round_1/agent_codex_1/stdout.log:31:    "claim": "`withdrawUSDTfromCmp` ignores Compound's `redeemUnderlying` return code, and `redeemInternal` responds to any resulting cash shortfall by shrinking `redeemAmount` to `cashAvailToWithdraw` while still burning the original `redeemTokens` amount.",
/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/depusdt_levusdc_p5_25_124/rounds/round_1/agent_codex_1/stdout.log:34:      "A user calls `redeem(redeemTokens, 0)` while the market needs to pull USDT back from Compound.",
/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/depusdt_levusdc_p5_25_124/rounds/round_1/agent_codex_1/stdout.log:53:    "impact": "Searchers can sandwich these swaps and extract value from the protocol or lev users. In the borrow path, the market records the full USDT debt while the lev side may receive materially less USDC than expected.",
/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/depusdt_levusdc_p5_25_124/rounds/round_1/agent_codex_1/stdout.log:56:      "Front-run to skew the USDT/USDC Curve price.",
/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/depusdt_levusdc_p5_25_124/rounds/round_1/agent_codex_1/stdout.log:74:    "claim": "`supplyUSDT2Cmp` uses `safeApprove` and then ignores Compound's `mint` return value. If `mint` returns an error code without consuming the allowance, the allowance remains non-zero and every later call to `safeApprove` for cUSDT reverts.",
